{"tid":2144202,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張竹君：不清楚中山紀念公園體育館用作實驗室詳細安排","createTime":"2020-08-07T14:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T14:24:45.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d1181ce9ada2879fc834ae3dc02be45e73765e2e","tid":2144202,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:21:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542429-20200807.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542429-20200807.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=1Tw5YvH57m5vrKXwbFhC6Amr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=3719f063\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542429-20200807.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=572e0b05\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542429-20200807.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君表示，不清楚有關採用鼻咽拭子，以及中山紀念公園體育館用作火眼實驗室的詳細安排，措施的細節由有關決策局敲定，衞生署無具體詳情。<br />\n<br />\n張竹君日前曾提及，全民檢測要考慮衞生防護中心及醫療系統的承受能力，政府將展開全民自願免費檢測，被問到目前醫療系統是否已有足夠承受力，張竹君說，有關當局為高危群組檢測本來已對醫療系統造成壓力，要視乎全民檢測結果，才能作出評估。"},{"pid":"203f6b449f1b18857a1246c1f07e30878e932263","tid":2144202,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:22:27.000Z","msg":"中國DNA收集隊係咪已經完全不受香港監管？<br />\n<br />\n張竹君完全不被知會做緊乜？"},{"pid":"5fc67fafc1f93a4cf2a9afba280c1022487d08ad","tid":2144202,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T14:24:45.000Z","msg":"柒婆勾結支那勢力自己搭個雞棚出嚟<br />\n架空香港醫護人員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}